data.description:
Welcome to your new home! This charming high and dry home is TURN KEY. (Roof is 2021, Hot Water Heater 2023) Meticulously maintained and updated, It boasts 3 bedrooms and 1.5 baths. New vinyl flooring that extends throughout the main living area and the upgraded bathrooms. The spacious kitchen has been updated with new cabinetry, stainless steel appliances, and beautiful granite countertops. The whole house has been freshly painted in a soft and bright beach-inspired color palette. A bright and versatile Florida room adds extra space for living. The backyard is expansive and comes fully fenced, providing both privacy and security. Lush landscaping adorns the front, creating a warm and inviting curb appeal. This home has undergone an energy-efficient makeover, including blown-in attic insulation, weather sealing for doors, solar screens for windows and a whole-home ventilation fan. Has Large Attached Utility Shed. The HVAC system is 2011 with a new blower 2023 The hot water heater is 2023. The rolled roof was replaced in 2021.
All info intended to be accurate but can't be guaranteed.
